Hi all, we've been having issues with some deals synced over the ecommerce bridge api v1.
Some of the deals will sync but they won't be assigned a pipeline or stage. Everything else syncs fine and the same logic is used to sync everything so not sure what could be going wrong.

I posted the same issue to the HubSpot community board with examples a week ago but there hasn't been any activity on it.
Hi <@UMEGEQ1GS> have you made any changes or edits in the deal stage name or added some additional deal stages ?
